Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中華聯邦的諸位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機情局的作戰計劃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 在巴別塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏挑這個日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今雖不認為黑色騎士團殘黨還能有何作為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那個ZERO已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別偷懶 11區的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標已到達 和預想一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由B3進入第5大門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次會出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出現就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都冒險放他去租界外沿部了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你只要送我來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天還是非法的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不止警告處分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕什麼警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過為什麼 哥哥不是為了錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問 是為了和更強的人對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不過是無聊的消遣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 今天萬眾矚目的兄弟對決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倖存的會是哥哥 還是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的比賽已連續進行了10輪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs24}哥哥 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不好嗎 一目瞭然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 開懷享樂的是我們布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣力受人恥笑的是11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算假裝無視 結果也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區輸了兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木首相和ZERO都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有實力還謀什麼反…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是11區人 而您是布里塔尼亞的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更不用這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭炫耀身份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒實力的人必須忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使錯在對方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把你們的價值觀強加於我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看你的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的「獵兔」收穫頗豐 真是可喜可賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敗者沒有人權
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安定因素 發生糾紛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怪就怪自己投錯胎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝陛下也這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉強食 這就是世界的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 是黑社會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為自己就算掠食者了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生 這是大人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 大人的世界和學生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰才是掠食者 用這個弄個明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國際象棋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生真是不諳世事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒未必
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗王者先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這個世界是赫赫有名的棋手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知道還來挑戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是ZERO還在 誰怕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別提那個叛徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO才不是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什麼內情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內情？大決戰中指揮官跑了還要什麼內情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何 ZERO已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.66,0:10:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗王者居然輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來弱肉的是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這事要是傳出去 我可就丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒興趣四處炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 學生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說你出千的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出千？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.68,0:10:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下棋怎麼出千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 偽造點證據吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骯髒的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相可不值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用飛船 垂死掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機密情報局 瓦爾哈拉七號行動開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Comment: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨11區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好隆重的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過聽說ZERO已經死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.88,0:11:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要讓中華聯邦的各位理解我們布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣比較明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地直截了當嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請交出您腰上的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治安可以保證 這種老古董…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星刻 太無禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是要讓各位理解我們中華聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣比較明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 目標跟丟了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我們正準備突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲擊巴別塔的恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎持有數架Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰開始同時 周邊已清理完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 進入第7階段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 卡拉雷斯總督…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方管理層無視就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是奉皇帝陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11區的走樓梯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團的殘黨怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 都怪我沒抓好他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別介意 卜部他們正在找
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:13:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非 是對我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心 絕對能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯真是 連羅洛都拖下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說吧 你是擔心魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅…羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不通 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 一定要救他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少應該能救出唯一的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點力量我應該也有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖分子干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.24,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 連11區人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還執著於ZERO那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要殺我嗎 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算逃也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接你了 魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的敵人是布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我訂過契約吧 我們是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契約？共犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我瞭解 真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的…我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯…魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 人還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修·蘭佩洛奇同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務？說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直在監視你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6點59分起床
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7點12分和弟弟一起邊看新聞邊吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視聽內容無思想性偏向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8點45分上學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未出席班會和第一堂課 在屋頂看書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二堂物理課…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是今天的…我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是誘餌的飼養日記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘餌？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說陷阱也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了引出那個魔女 C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可沒興趣跟誘餌說太多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 該處分掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就沒有目擊者了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處分？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…要死？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明不白的 這麼輕易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃離這裡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝過世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音 是剛才的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量你已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被封鎖在忘卻之籠中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻 解除封印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如荊棘般刺入我生活的焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是虛偽的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不求你原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的回答嗎 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,處分我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女的還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 明明射穿了心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若無力是罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那力量就是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇就是罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友誼就算是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼罪惡正義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誘餌只有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼也給你們一條路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯路修·V·布里塔尼亞下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賜你們 一死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天起 我心中就無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不自然的虛偽生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯離的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.69,0:21:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶被篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家畜般的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.56,0:21:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真實一直在追求我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 錯的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界將會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等候多時了 ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請下令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.95,0:21:38.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破壞世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死ZERO的 將是我
Comment: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不饒恕 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的記憶是僅屬於我的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保持自我的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.95,0:23:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而有人卻將其踐踏 視為馴養家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者作為餌食 蔑視至極
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,償還的時刻到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.64,0:24:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO回歸這一事實的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要讓布里塔尼亞回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虛偽的統治 已不再需要
